      "MindSettler is committed to providing a safe, encouraging, and structured psycho-education and mental well-being experience.",

      "NO REFUND situations:",

      "a. If a therapist has been assigned to you and you decide not to proceed with the session, no refund will be provided.",

      "b. If you are unhappy with the therapy or the therapeutic approach, MindSettler may consider adjusting the methods or approach where appropriate. However, no refund will be provided, and any previously used session time will not be reimbursed.",

      "c. If you have completed your booked sessions and are not satisfied, no refund will be given. You may choose to continue by booking additional sessions or packages.",

      "d. All sessions must be completed within the validity period communicated at the time of booking. Any unused sessions after the validity period expires will be forfeited and are not eligible for a refund. Scheduling sessions is the responsibility of the user.",

      "e. If a therapist needs to reschedule a session, this does not make the session or package eligible for a refund.",

      "f. Cancelling a package or session mid-subscription will not be eligible for a partial or full refund.",

      "g. Sessions are generally scheduled once per week. While users may request preferred time slots, final scheduling depends on therapist availability.",

      "h. It is the userâ€™s responsibility to coordinate and complete sessions within the applicable time period. If you face difficulties in scheduling, you must reach out to MindSettler through the official contact channels.",

